## Message Templates

### Employee Notification - Initial
```
Subject: Important Update from [Company]

[Greeting],

We want to inform you about a [situation type] that occurred [when].

What happened: [Brief, factual description]

What we're doing: [Actions being taken]

What you should do: [Clear instructions]

We will provide another update by [time].

[Contact information for questions]

[Signature]
```

### Customer Notification
```
Subject: Important Information from [Company]

Dear [Customer],

We are writing to inform you about [situation] that may affect [how it affects them].

What happened: [Brief, factual description without technical jargon]

How this affects you: [Impact to them]

What we're doing: [Actions and timeline]

What you can do: [If any action required]

We apologize for any inconvenience and appreciate your patience.

For questions: [Contact information]

Sincerely,
[Executive signature]
```

### Media Statement
```
[Company] Statement Regarding [Incident]

[City, Date] - [Company name] is responding to [incident type] that occurred [when].

[Brief, factual description of what happened]

[What company is doing in response]

[Expression of concern for those affected if applicable]

[Forward-looking statement]

For more information, contact:
[Media contact name]
[Contact information]

###
```

