## Social Media Guidelines

### During a Crisis
- [ ] Acknowledge the situation quickly
- [ ] Direct to official channels for updates
- [ ] Don't speculate or share unverified information
- [ ] Monitor for questions and misinformation
- [ ] Respond with empathy
- [ ] Pause scheduled posts if appropriate

### Response Template
"We're aware of [situation] and are actively working to [action].
For updates, please visit [link]. Thank you for your patience."

---

